                            <comment id="69099" author="schlaufuchs" created="Fri, 5 Aug 2011 21:09:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I meant we don&apos;t have qualifiers for that beans as they are configured in xml files and are coded in ancient times before annotations became common. So we have a lot of places where we wire them by name instead of type. I&apos;m quite sure that the qualifier doesn&apos;t trigger wire by name, or am I wrong? Does the @Resource annotation work here?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
